  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where I was in the-- I was in the-- almost in my house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was take a look what happened my house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Warsaw was bombarded with merciless-- without mercy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They see the houses crumble.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People running like crazy from [? our ?] house to another.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Our section was better off because was a Polish section.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Jewish section was destroyed seat-- one street by another street, and so it was a terrible situation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Is no water, no food, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "People running like crazy, asking question [? and answer. ?] We was on the station.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "On the station-- we-- we located on the station, they call this [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [? find ?] this [POLISH] was trains, but they go out east, to east Poland, to the border.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we go to-- they tell us to go to the trains, and the trains with ammunition, they started to go back to this point on Bug, to the Bug, to the Bug.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My family was in the-- in-- in the house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in the house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what I remember, what I know, this all families living in-- in Warsaw, they was a special-- special order from the Germans that I find [? up ?] and put in all these people to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This a couple months later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is what I know, because I-- I tell [? him ?] the story how this happened I-- because I was in the-- I was in the train, and the train go with ammunition, went to Bug.",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
